Micro.blog app
<https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/micro-blog/id1253201335?ls=3D1&mt=3D8> for
iOS.

 =E2=80=A2 There's an official Micro.blog app for Mac too
<http://help.micro.blog/2017/mac-version/>.

 =E2=80=A2 If you are looking for people to follow in the Micro.blog timeli=
ne,
check out the Discover section, found in the apps and on the Micro.blog
website.

 =E2=80=A2 Hosted microblogs can use custom domain names, i.e. yourname.com=
. See
this help page <http://help.micro.blog/2015/custom-domains/> for more
information. Choose "New..." =E2=86=92 "New microblog site" on Micro.blog t=
o
start a microblog.

 =E2=80=A2 We have a community on Slack. Introduce yourself and your blog i=
n the
#followme channel, or discuss blogging topics with other Micro.blog users.
You can sign up for Slack here <https://micro.blog/slack>.

 If you ever have any questions or feedback, don't hesitate to let us know
at help@micro.blog <mailto:help@micro.blog>, or just reply to this email.

           Micro.blog is a platform for indie microblogs. help.micro.blog
<http://help.micro.blog/>

